{"tid":591442,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇LG G7都係M額？","createTime":"2018-03-13T14:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T04:41:53.000Z","uid":1130,"like":3,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"0498145c795a7152a0bb1f2c25da9bbb64cf6a2e","tid":591442,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/13/lg-g7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2Flg-g7%2F&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b9291a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/13/lg-g7/</a><br />\n<br />\n各大手機廠商紛紛在 MWC 推出旗下最新 2018 年旗艦機，而 LG 在 MWC 並沒有推出 G 系列新一代的 LG G7，而據韓國媒體 ETNews 最新報導，LG 已經計劃在 4 月尾或 5 月發佈 LG G7，並於 5 月中正式開售。ETNews 更提供了 LG G7 的外觀以及規格數據，其外觀與 iPhone X 非常相似。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/1050649_20180312171445_758_0001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F1050649_20180312171445_758_0001.jpg&h=80e84a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而隨著驍龍 845 處理器以及 RAM 以及容量的升級，價格預計將比以前的 LG G6（899,800 韓元）增加 10 萬韓元 (~HKD$7370)。LG 電子和三家移動電信服務提供商將於 5 月份正式推出 &lsquo;G7&middot;G7 Plus&rsquo;。 LG 電子擁有高端智能手機品牌（G&middot;V），高端智能手機品牌的整合預計將在明年開始。<br />\n<br />\nG7 將螢幕&ldquo;缺口設計&rdquo;（M 字額）應用於（OLED）顯示器。這是蘋果應用於 iPhone X 的首款設計，前置攝像頭傳感器位於凹槽處，最大限度地減少了邊框厚度。隨著 5 月份 G7 的推出，預計下半年智能手機發佈時間的變化將不可避免。 它很可能在 11 月份推出 G7S 或 V40。"},{"pid":"bee383c2497792d6007c1caf9593c8516b1a8fc8","tid":591442,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"好平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b52f958ad655233a281ec96efca1eb1d9a79082","tid":591442,"uid":37688,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"LG 咁搞隨時仲快收皮過htc"},{"pid":"ce69a89e50220cf8da265a5a6a289715c4d7ec9f","tid":59