預計將在明年開始。<br />\n<br />\nG7 將螢幕&ldquo;缺口設計&rdquo;（M 字額）應用於（OLED）顯示器。這是蘋果應用於 iPhone X 的首款設計，前置攝像頭傳感器位於凹槽處，最大限度地減少了邊框厚度。隨著 5 月份 G7 的推出，預計下半年智能手機發佈時間的變化將不可避免。 它很可能在 11 月份推出 G7S 或 V40。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你即將進入內容農場：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newmobilelife.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e5fa80bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.newmobilelife.com</a><br />\n要繼續嗎？若是感到厭煩，放棄也是一種選擇啊。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.etnews.com/20180312000327?mc=em_004_00001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnews.com%2F20180312000327%3Fmc%3Dem_004_00001&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fc1eaef8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnews.com/20180312000327?mc=em_004_00001</a>"},{"pid":"f3525bf8d903aeacc214079de5c6a90195904560","tid":591442,"uid":107023,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"G7 可以自由 set full screen M字額 或變回正常平額模式，用家決定"},{"pid":"05be92927f8a1b296d4724b740d7193b9f9df4ce","tid":591442,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3525bf8d903aeacc214079de5c6a90195904560","tid":591442,"uid":107023,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"G7 可以自由 set full screen M字額 或變回正常平額模式，用家決定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:10:47.000Z","msg":"張rumor有相機同sensor係M字額嗰個位"},{"pid":"1dccfcbbf571bdcb5a421bd41394955e8b6d2cf7","tid":591442,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05be92927f8a1b296d4724b740d7193b9f9df4ce","tid":591442,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3525bf8d903aeacc214079de5c6a90195904560","tid":591442,"uid":107023,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"G7 可以自由 set full screen M字額 或變回正常平額模式，用家決